Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:08.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So... why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:13.56,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Since elves stand out, disguising \Nourselves as beasts allow us to blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.04,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,These are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:17.15,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,They act like the real thing once equipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:19.99,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You called them cosplay items, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:23.05,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,They have the ability to conceal \Nthe traits of one's species.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:24.71,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Er, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:30.21,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,I never dreamed stuff I mostly made \Nfor a laugh would come in so handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:33.06,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,By the way, Shin, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.09,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.09,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Do they look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:41.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:45.15,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,W-We're going to see Schweid, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.22,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Let us hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.89,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I've never seen her like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.74,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,That aside, I didn't think\N I'd get to see {\i0}him{\i1} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.53,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,Kilmont is an allied nation of Farnid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:05.58,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,And representing them at the funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:10.56,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,was my former support character \NSchweid the high dragnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:48.02,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Representatives of the various \Nnations are staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:55.90,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Is Schweid a monarch like Girart?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:03:01.11,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,No. Though he was the first emperor\Nof the Dragon Empire, Kilmont,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.16,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,he's cut ties with the imperial family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:07.91,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Ever since Kilmont stabilized, \Nhe has been living at his leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm surprised the people accepted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:14.64,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,The second and current emperor \Nwas originally meant to be the first,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.67,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,but he was injured during\Nthe nation's founding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.42,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So Schweid was just a stand-in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:24.18,Default,BUTLER,0,0,0,,I shall fetch Lord Schweid. Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.54,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,I have a meeting to attend, \Nso I will be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.43,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Please let Cuore know if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.30,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,You are dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.71,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Uh, long time no see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:58.52,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,I am delighted that you have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:03.84,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,I shall serve you once more \Nand be the spear that pierces your foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:07.10,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,Ah, right. He's {\i0}that{\i1} kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:11.66,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Listen, I'll tell you what I told Schnee.\NWe finally get to see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.60,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let's take it easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.85,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:20.61,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Schweid, if Shin says it's okay,\N then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.41,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,Not "Master," but "Shin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.61,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.81,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:32.54,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,Very well. If that is how things are,\NI shall conduct myself at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:36.50,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,By the way, Schnee, \Nwhy are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.44,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,To suit Shin's tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.76,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Could you not give him the wrong idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:48.26,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,I see. So Girart passed on a satisfied man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.51,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,That sounds just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.52,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,A warrior until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.78,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,So, Shin, what will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.68,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I've researched all I can\Nat the libraries here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.32,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,so I'll hit the sacred place next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.33,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,I will be returning to Kilmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.16,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,Allow me to join you after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.00,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we partied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:15.17,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,Indeed. We can use telepathy\Nto keep in contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:18.38,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Welp, we'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.74,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.18,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,It can't be! Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yup. It's your personal weapon, Nagizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.39,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,It's been ages since I held it last,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.56,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,but nothing could feel\Nmore natural in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:38.18,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I took care of the maintenance for you.\NSee for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.62,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,Impressive work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.82,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,Though it seems more powerful \Nthan the Nagizuki I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.76,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:51.28,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,My mana control has improved \Nsince I repaired Girart's equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.58,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, \Nshe's now five times stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:57.41,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,Your abilities have grown\Nin such a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.83,Default,SCHWEID,0,0,0,,That's incredible, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'd like to get my adventurer \Nrank up to around C.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.32,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,Goblin slaying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We can do this as a day trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.48,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,Um, would it be all right if I joined you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.55,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll take care of my \Nremaining work once I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.41,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:33.61,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,I'm investigating the Raluah Forest \Nwhere you held your duel the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:36.66,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,To make sure it's regrowing properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:40.13,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Mind if I tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.49,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,What? You could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:46.55,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Since I was part of that duel, \NI want to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.68,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,In that case, I'd love to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We'll each take one. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:56.81,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.88,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,And that's one job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:14.95,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Incredible. We made a mess of this place, \Nbut it's already back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:20.21,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,We're going to examine the regenerated trees \Nand look for anything unnatural in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.63,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,If you spot any unusual herbs growing, \Nplease pick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.96,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:35.65,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We finished the job. \NMind confirming it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:39.95,Default,RECEPTION,0,0,0,,Very well. Also, I have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:40.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:47.20,Default,RECEPTION,0,0,0,,It's from Barlux, guild master \Nof our Bayrelicht branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.11,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Barlux? Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I've been summoned \Nby the palace in Bayrelicht.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.45,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It says to head there as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.58,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,What does the palace want with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.35,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.39,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You don't have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.08,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:10.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, okay, maybe one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:14.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I might have to take care of this\Nbefore working on my rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.49,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.55,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,So will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:22.06,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,I wish I could go with you, \Nbut I can't leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.40,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.55,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,There's something I want to give Wolfgang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.44,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Could you let me know when he's free?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.82,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,You have something for my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.77,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,Father, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:41.74,Default,CUORE,0,0,0,,Shin wishes to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.86,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Show him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:50.04,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Don't be. This is also part\N of my kingly duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.59,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Now, more importantly, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:57.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sorry for the short notice, but I need \Nto leave for Bayrelicht right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.30,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I thought I'd give you these before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.10,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.81,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Girart's Death Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.11,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I've already changed the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.56,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You can transfer them to whoever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.11,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,I'd heard they were destroyed in your duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.68,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm the one who made Death Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Repairing them was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:22.62,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:28.00,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Girart asked me to give them to you \Nonce the duel was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:31.24,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,The first king wanted me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.88,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Mind making sure they're good to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.38,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.39,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,These are unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.39,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's up to you who inherits them next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.05,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,I accept that responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Okay, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.87,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You intend to teleport?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.16,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Perhaps to where the Moon Sanctum was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:10.92,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. A wagon would take too long, \Nand that area is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:14.54,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Another crystal? How extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.44,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,All right. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.52,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Someone's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm glad I used a stealth skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:31.69,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Perhaps they think the Moon Sanctum \Nwill reappear in this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.94,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,People must have long forgotten\N that it could be moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.66,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Y-You won't disappear, will you, Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.22,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:47.05,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I just... grew a bit nervous that\Nthat day may come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.19,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Schnee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.56,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It's unfounded, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.84,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You're going to be left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.76,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey, wait. I'm the one Barlux summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.11,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,So why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:06.35,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I couldn't imagine what it's like to wait \Nfor someone who might never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:09.48,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.45,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.61,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:15.48,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Elves and humans have totally \Ndifferent perceptions of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.04,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,If we wanted to wait, why wouldn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.25,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.86,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:25.87,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,For long-lived species like us, losing our \Nreason to live is the gateway to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.12,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So thinking about it too hard \Ngets you into trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:34.29,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,That's right. If you're going to think, \Nput your mind to something more useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.26,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Besides, it throws me off \Nwhen you suddenly get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:41.76,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Could you not make it sound like I'm cavalier\Nabout everything all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.51,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You do get serious \Nabout the strangest things, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Shaddup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:51.06,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Shin, it's good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I received a summons from the guild master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.52,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,We'll let him know you're here. \NOne moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.63,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Cilica, could you go get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.96,Default,CILICA,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.91,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Do you know what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:08.42,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,No. We're not told that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:12.55,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,But I did expect you'd be summoned soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:13.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:17.17,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Because you're hardly an ordinary adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:24.18,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,You're always traveling with beautiful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:28.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I-I have male acquaintances, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.56,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Oh? I've never seen you speaking to one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.60,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That can't be true. There's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Wilhelm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.11,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We've worked together before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:38.82,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.82,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Is that true, Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.42,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It wasn't an official job, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Why did everyone go quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.98,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,He rarely forms parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:13:00.34,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,They say his combat strength is S-rank, \Nbut there are many rumors about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.29,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Folks find him difficult to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:06.31,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's easily misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:10.59,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Wilhelm himself is an \Nexceptional man, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:12.30,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.49,Default,CILICA,0,0,0,,Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.93,Default,CILICA,0,0,0,,We're ready for you. This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.86,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,You're here sooner than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.61,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I was already headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:29.87,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,Sorry to rush you. This is Arahd the mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.62,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,I am Arahd Royl. A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.29,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,He appraises gems for the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:41.38,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,He assessed the Skullface gem \Nyou brought in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.88,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,My name is Shin. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:49.89,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,As I said in my message,\Nthe palace has summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,May I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.02,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,Before that, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:14:00.81,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,Are you aware that a sword \Nflew into the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:04.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I heard {\i1}something{\i0} flew into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.44,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:09.28,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,It was a massive white sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:13.27,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,On top of that, it crashed into the bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:15.45,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,of the second princess of Bayrelicht.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.42,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,It caused quite the stir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.09,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.30,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,Fortunately, no one was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.42,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,The issue is the sword itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:31.17,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,Its elemental enchantment \Nand base materials are quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.84,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's comparable \Nto the kingdom's royal sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.68,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:45.29,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,The gem from the Skullface you defeated \Nalso possessed powerful mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.82,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,I heard it was a rather high level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.68,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,G-Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.58,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,They definitely know who's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:58.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,How did you manage to figure out\N that I was involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:01.65,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,Someone was trying to find out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.09,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,They got wind of the gem, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:08.34,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,As its appraiser, I was asked \Nto examine the sword as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:14.97,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,There were traces of mana left on it\Ndistinct from the sword's own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:18.58,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,It matched the mana from the gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:22.86,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,So it's like fantasy DNA identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.32,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,From there, they followed the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:31.61,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,When they discovered you were the one \Nwho brought the gem, you were summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:35.74,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,Given the circumstances, \Nthe guild couldn't keep your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:39.21,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Considering what they knew, \Nyou couldn't fool them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.50,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's not on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:44.77,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,Fortunately, because you had a letter \Nof introduction from the Moon Sanctum,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.98,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,the situation isn't any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.91,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,Now, getting down to business...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:54.51,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,The second princess, Her Highness Rionne \Nherself, is the one who summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:55.66,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.49,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,This incident piqued her interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:04.02,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Is she going to hold me responsible \Nfor nearly injuring royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.02,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,No, you won't be punished for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:11.03,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,The princess has slain Skullfaces before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.80,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,Based on her experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.15,Default,BUTLER,0,0,0,,she's convinced everyone that \Nyou'd have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.03,Default,BUTLER,0,0,0,,but to use full force against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:22.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I appreciate that, but then \Nwhat exactly does she want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.65,Default,BARLUX,0,0,0,,I don't know the answer to that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:28.92,Default,ARAHD,0,0,0,,Politicians are nasty creatures, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's what they told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.17,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.68,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You sent a sword flying into the palace? \NWhy would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.00,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's not like I did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:44.94,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,So Shin's just amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.15,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,In some ways, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:51.67,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Perhaps they wish to press you\N into their service
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.20,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,or have you marry an important noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.70,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,M-Marry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:17:00.58,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes. They say a nation's power is proportional\Nto its high-ranking chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.83,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I believe they'll aggressively \Ntry to recruit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.64,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I suddenly don't feel like going anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:09.95,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I doubt there's any problem with you \Nrefusing to enter their service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:10.84,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.69,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,As your party members, \Nwe'd suffer a great loss if you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:17.09,Default,SCHEEN,0,0,0,,That should be reason enough \Nto turn them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.88,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,But on the other hand, \Nif they want to marry me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:24.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Refusing stuff like that without \Na good reason only causes more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:28.23,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,On that front, you could tell them\N I am your fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.98,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey, yeah, I could say I'm already spoken for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:35.17,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Depending on the circumstances, \Nyou could even say you're betrothed to Tiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.88,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,T-To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.62,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Oh, would you not like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.74,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,As long as we're just pretending...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.50,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Then Yuzuha will be Shin's fiancée, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.52,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Wait, Yuzuha. We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.75,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It'd destroy me socially!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.81,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We're just pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.25,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's only make-believe. It's not for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.13,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,You're not going to mate with Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:58.38,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Don't say stuff like that in that form!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.10,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Mate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.85,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Why don't we all calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:08.32,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I've been summoned by the second princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:09.27,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,My name is Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.16,Default,GUARD,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:14.04,Default,GUARD,0,0,0,,I'll retrieve your escort. One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.30,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.28,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:26.07,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,Excuse me. You're Shin\N the adventurer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.55,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:32.39,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,I am Gadras. Princess Rionne \Nasked me to fetch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.42,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.93,Sign_Basic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an4\fs10\b1\shad0\3c&H47495C&\c&HDBE8E7&\pos(383.938,207.213)}Dark Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.93,Sign_Basic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an4\fs12\b1\shad0\3c&H47495C&\c&HDBE8E7&\pos(463.211,202.122)}Gadras Jarre
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.23,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,Level 188...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.93,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,They sent one of the kingdom's \Nmost powerful men to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:50.44,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,We're here. Princess Rionne is just inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.16,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,It's Gadras. I've brought Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:55.94,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.77,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:13.46,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I am Rionne Sytrail Bayrelicht, \Nsecond princess of this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.34,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:20.21,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,My name is Shin. \NThank you for inviting me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:23.27,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I care little for etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.97,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Feel free to call me Rionne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.22,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Very well, Rionne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.47,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,Your Highness, that's hardly proper\Nfor someone you've just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.96,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,You've confused him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.87,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,We may fight side by side eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.11,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,It beats building walls \Njust because I'm royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.29,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon, Shin,\N but this is simply how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.49,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,No need for formality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:46.49,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Uh, may I ask why I was summoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:52.00,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I'm sure Barlux gave you an overview, \Nbut it's about the Skullface.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.26,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,You recognize this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:05.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's the sword the Skullface was wielding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.01,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I imagine it was quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:15.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, yes. My own weapon \Nwas destroyed in the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.81,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.36,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,At least that much is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.86,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I knew you were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.11,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Different, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:30.04,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Most adventurers like you who suddenly \Ndistinguish themselves are chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:37.59,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,When we determine one to be rather powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.88,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,we typically summon you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:44.77,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Some have used the opportunity \Nto plot assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.56,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,How frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:50.01,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Some suspected you would as well, \Nbut you seem safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.39,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I don't recall saying anything \Nthat would clear such suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.90,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Of course you didn't. \NI'm going off my instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:56.90,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.40,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,You've shown your colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:04.68,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I mean, I doubt anyone would\Naccept that without more concrete proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:08.38,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,That's not a problem.\NI possess the skill "Intuition."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:11.79,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,My hunches have never been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.37,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,Is that how Intuition works?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:18.54,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,Is the Intuition skill \Nenhancing her woman's intuition?
